"""Run reno (release notes manager) without needing a riot venv.

Usage:
    scripts/reno new <slug>           # create a new release note
    scripts/reno lint                 # validate existing notes
    scripts/reno report               # generate changelog output
    uv run --script scripts/reno ...  # same, explicit uv invocation
"""
